{"tid":1569633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放低道德包袱 效法藍絲 全面開戰","createTime":"2019-09-14T16:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:11:04.000Z","uid":212255,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"03eeafa2d792e81b2f5cfc90431fe8711b720df1","tid":1569633,"uid":212255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"online主線攻略<br />\n<br />\n戰術<br />\n快閃 hit and run<br />\n使用致命武力都唔割<br />\n而且鼓勵使用高攻武器<br />\n<br />\n明明我地人多（齋計香港）<br />\n點解要挨打<br />\n藍絲收兩舊水出黎 如果會受傷<br />\n一定少好多人出<br />\n增加維穩成本<br />\n中國人最欺善怕惡<br />\n<br />\n今日淘大直播有個手足講左句說話好型<br />\n沙士我地都未驚 使驚你！<br />\n<br />\n而家既情況係<br />\n我方一直損兵折將 肉體心靈同經濟都受傷<br />\n敵方以逸待勞 仲不斷有ot錢<br />\n場仗唔使打都知邊個會贏<br />\n<br />\n唔改變而家既狀況 香港人不如早d 認輸算<br />\n<br />\n另外雖然話唔割蓆<br />\n但我真係好想大家認清左膠<br />\n左膠其實係偽黃<br />\n出手保護藍絲<br />\n其實即係敵人黎<br />\n要記住對敵人仁慈就係對自己人殘忍"},{"pid":"ae53297a940c2db4345d67425eda30b3cdcb4e43","tid":1569633,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d43900b1d29052698598b78486f88dd6084f2ae2","tid":1569633,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09646b3e2e2e0f2fe5d805e8e7595f1ffd4bfca","tid":1569633,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日港島見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n現正聲明915網民超自發流水式英領請願，只對英國政府有2項訴求：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 1. 對中國無視聯合聲明採取行動；<br />\n 2. 承認一國兩制遭受破壞；</span></span><br />\n<br />\n915並無邀請任何人以組織名義到場 及 無邀請政治背景人物。面斥不雅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5NoYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5NoYN.jpg&h=6894a64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvUKrb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvUKrb8.jpg&h=ec6b4d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmgkPKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmgkPKt.jpg&h=eac5cb50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12點英領和平請願<br />\n灰磚範圍 英國領土</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2點打後 銅鑼灣自由活動!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【國際戰線】又係我，前英領職員，915見（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565523</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c12d01fd55e0bdee9c3bfdc766af182dca5c70be","tid":1569633,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑冷水<br />\n好多連儂撚連你想組隊都會阻止你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地覺得勇武啲人係冇撚腦淨係會比人拉送頭<br />\n連PLAN都未撚聽就可以咬定你會比人拉<br />\n所以今次今日都仲未見到有地區力量出現"},{"pid":"c168403fab641ad2dfbd74ecd00ba7452d3a0cb0","tid":1569633,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"必推"},{"pid":"d9a59dcbc4b9fa4267260d1a3748582453e020eb","tid":1569633,"uid":135067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2