if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣"},{"pid":"bc9ef9c61f1457ad378b262ce9e4c7475432cca8","tid":1569633,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c12d01fd55e0bdee9c3bfdc766af182dca5c70be","tid":1569633,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑冷水<br />\n好多連儂撚連你想組隊都會阻止你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地覺得勇武啲人係冇撚腦淨係會比人拉送頭<br />\n連PLAN都未撚聽就可以咬定你會比人拉<br />\n所以今次今日都仲未見到有地區力量出現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"仲有咩清左再貼<br />\n前期藍絲冇組織就係<br />\n縱撚到班友咁<br />\n藍絲宜家見你成班友廢成咁單拖都會拆<br />\n相反你單拖去整牆實比人打撚死"},{"pid":"a162b191f6df985a3ad17d8e72568b5a420b6866","tid":1569633,"uid":41411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"my name"},{"pid":"70fcf168827e73905f67c9f652ec0879fa6f9950","tid":1569633,"uid":47208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要對準政權"},{"pid":"59e29fdf51a7d419760f50df31a26711961a3ec4","tid":1569633,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:40:29.000Z","msg":"日本南北朝時代的武將楠木正成將軍壯烈犧牲後，旗幟上留有「非、理、法、權、天」五個字。這五個字是什麼意思呢？<br />\n<br />\n非，就是不對的事情。所以，「非」不能勝過「理」，這是當然的。<br />\n<br />\n理，不能勝過「法」。例如，在法官之前，即使你講說多少道理，但是他也可能說：「我知道你有很多的理由，不過你做的這件事情不合法。」所以，在法律之前，道理也不算道理了。<br />\n<br />\n法，不能勝過「權」。例如，古代有權勢的人，他可以改變法令。就是今日，世界上也還有許多地方只講權力，沒有法制。<br />\n<br />\n權，不能勝過「天」。天，就是最高的真理，也就是因果的道理。一個人權力再大，就算是逃脫得了法律的制裁，但是在因果、天理之前，必定也要受報。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">汝欲和平，必先備戰<br />\n替天行道</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"79e38ea718752efd986597af4cd9386b788db7b3","tid":1569633,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"必須承認藍屍入面有唔少係真心, 而呢班人就好似我地就算一直比黑警打咁, 只會越打越出, 然之後每次再出黎都會加強武裝, 更何況佢地打人傷人真係冇成本<br />\n我覺得要諗埋民眾鬥民眾既可能性"},{"pid":"46b359527154e64bf19f1a0b6170cd39cb243626","tid":1569633,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:42:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc41a4f20ec155393e7fae5244f947c061810078","tid":1569633,"uid":212255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e38ea718752efd986597af4cd9386b788db7b3","tid":1569633,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"必須承認藍屍入面有唔少係真心, 而呢班人就好似我地就算一直比黑警打咁, 只會越打越出, 然之後每次再出黎都會加強武裝, 更何況佢地打人傷人真係冇成本<br />\n我覺得要諗埋民眾鬥民眾既可能性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔好怕咩野民眾鬥民眾<br />\n怕是但一樣野都會輸<br />\n要鬥贏咁卑鄙既敵人<br />\n未怕要卑鄙過佢<br />\n但最少要勇悍過對方"},{"pid":"4c5d2b638713e197c399b41ce729870d14cfe0fe","tid":1569633,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"啱啊 打藍絲唔洗坐監嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打差佬就要<br />\n<br />\n講緊gta"},{"pid":"212ceda42e75892501fa3e685fb888a386fd8e59","tid":1569633,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DNgrNs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DNgrNs.png&h=79213bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抗爭社運mv - Protest Times   Never back down<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bXgpGFTuK54\" data-sr-url=\"https://